msgid ""
"Reserve stock for all items in the cart during checkout. Creates temporary "
"stock reservations with 15-minute TTL. Returns list of reservation IDs to be"
" used during order creation."
msgstr ""
"Δέσμευση αποθέματος για όλα τα είδη του καλαθιού κατά το checkout. "
