msgstr "Λήψη πακέτου εξαγωγής δεδομένων GDPR"

#: .\user\views\data_export.py:39
msgid ""
"Returns the JSON bundle produced by the export task. The token is single-"
"scope, tied to one UserDataExport row, and expires 7 days after the export "
"was produced."
